{"tid":258120,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(台服)天外新開始","createTime":"2017-05-25T21:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T02:37:02.000Z","uid":45085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"763f50e7d3bf0c496742c68ab6d9c164f4d319d8","tid":258120,"uid":45085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T21:12:55.000Z","msg":"有巴打絲打新玩重玩既<br />\n可以入我地新家族<br />\n全部自己人<br />\n想入族既<br />\n(寄信)Game內唯一清泉<br />\n放心呢個族冇小圈子"},{"pid":"f4dc46716b44bf98cef3e0eafe659be02bce5944","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪有1.5 同工房"},{"pid":"9cad6b32752a041152ccd68de5e961c3c8b05aee","tid":258120,"uid":96732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T22:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fba40e7c6cc035a4dcd17f74112d5ec9e7339fd","tid":258120,"uid":93713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T23:29:08.000Z","msg":"太難升lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n<br />\n以前試過重玩， 比d 老手建議我買點再賣d 野出去拎一筆錢請人帶升，  要課金即刻唔想玩"},{"pid":"00cbe460b28049139afb3bcdb8be6926de0e6f27","tid":258120,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T00:46:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0653ff07038b0c2e514ddec714db70c17f12538f","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:33:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>太難升lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />     <br />\n<br />\n以前試過重玩， 比d 老手建議我買點再賣d 野出去拎一筆錢請人帶升，  要課金即刻唔想玩</blockquote><br />\n玩天外好難唔課金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋而家掛野真係賺唔到錢<br />\n比人帶升又要好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都有肯帶升既巴打絲打 睇下有無緣撞到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bfd8de877194b64ea8e802b6527f72e50744def","tid":258120,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T04:36:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會有巴打帶升到40先<br />\n<br />\n同埋仲有無隨任團"},{"pid":"747c9450bab3bfc6b04aee0c049c7d5f3d36f1d2","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會有巴打帶升到40先<br />\n<br />\n同埋仲有無隨任團</blockquote><br />\n我地可以幫帶40 (打地牢)<br />\n40後我地希望大家自力更新<br />\n我地亦都會有大腿帶大家做隨任 有意跟樓主所述之大頭 以便加入本家族<br />\n<br />\nps 做花要拉車 都要出力 唔可以做廢青 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手快有手慢無"},{"pid":"44dfba8aa5f78e46e813ea8412e7de033cd7460b","tid":258120,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"想知升lv係咪仲係咁難..果陣比錢升到隻術40lv 試下自己打發現打好耐都升唔到1lv.."},{"pid":"c44b07af78d0902236b8af91792d84af79b15182","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知升lv係咪仲係咁難..果陣比錢升到隻術40lv 試下自己打發現打好耐都升唔到1lv..</blockquote><br />\nYES 始於係免費SER 乜都減半<br />\n而家30LV或之前都叫有新手香食下 到30後就真係要燒錢買快香<br />\n搵人帶地牢都要預90W-120W 很貴 但30-&gt;40 2hr KO"},{"pid":"23f14ad395ea89490aac347d3933af98c07ba795","tid":258120,"uid":45085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知升lv係咪仲係咁難..果陣比錢升到隻術40lv 試下自己打發現打好耐都升唔到1lv..</blockquote><br />\nYES 始於係免費SER 乜都減半<br />\n而家30LV或之前都叫有新手香食下 到30後就真係要燒錢買快香<br />\n搵人帶地牢都要預90W-120W 很貴 但30-&gt;40 2hr KO</blockquote><br />\n有心玩就課金<br />\n150hkd都有3000w"},{"pid":"f81a80816ef767316841eca315f002ae47422506","tid":258120,"uid":46927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"買ac仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69927374c19ef74cbcfb667c9a79a0c784a7956e","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T06:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買ac仲平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實收AC好危險 <br />\n除對方願意提交切結書 <br />\n否則 賣家最後都可以向雷爵遞FORM(以個人真實資料)拎番個AC 仲要合法<br />\n無切結書 交易平台 雷爵都會懶理你<br />\n都已經有唔少人試過咁樣比人爆番AC"},{"pid":"c6bf840d44cea295a7675d23c82940193711b4dd","tid":258120,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T07:49:51.000Z","msg":"個族有無人有升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdeff67242310ef7f5d6338e502606de9c420c7f","tid":258120,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"幾多香港人玩緊"},{"pid":"2d331add6e3e20ab80bf2b80c7fe21c94784efc6","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:39:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個族有無人有升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nKEEP有隨任團 間中會帶升地牢"},{"pid":"ecb93e9a0f2b1eeaafedf8c267c931a1dcaf5c11","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多香港人玩緊</blockquote><br />\n而家個族都有10個活躍玩緊~ 都興趣就搵大頭加你地"},{"pid":"aa4610e6ca627128be734a37f948ac09fc5f686e","tid":258120,"uid":82816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知升lv係咪仲係咁難..果陣比錢升到隻術40lv 試下自己打發現打好耐都升唔到1lv..</blockquote><br />\n40除左頭幾LV打妖3仲有經<br />\n多數做隨機任到60"},{"pid":"2c33484fb559b0adf9dd6e5a8ff0d7ff92d880c3","tid":258120,"uid":82816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T09:49:24.000Z","msg":"隻gmae專養廢人/蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個淨係識企妖3等人帶 冇人帶就唔玩<br />\n年年帶到D人30幾40就消失晒<br />\n明明有方法賺錢靠自己包團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78986700b786e8412f8de31bf9f368cebf5e9aee","tid":258120,"uid":45085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"推呀推"},{"pid":"4bd4a0539b658789a261b6cbf60c350833e367f9","tid":258120,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隻gmae專養廢人/蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個淨係識企妖3等人帶 冇人帶就唔玩<br />\n年年帶到D人30幾40就消失晒<br />\n明明有方法賺錢靠自己包團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得佢哋既 新手啱啱玩咩都唔識<br />\n自然感受唔到個樂趣<br />\n想退天都好正常"},{"pid":"952268854ca7681a42987be088101a00b3198478","tid":258120,"uid":12802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隻gmae專養廢人/蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個淨係識企妖3等人帶 冇人帶就唔玩<br />\n年年帶到D人30幾40就消失晒<br />\n明明有方法賺錢靠自己包團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得佢哋既 新手啱啱玩咩都唔識<br />\n自然感受唔到個樂趣<br />\n想退天都好正常</blockquote><br />\n有D職仲要係80LV 先享受到真正既樂趣 好易令人放棄 D經咁少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7740f4dc11ad1ba0c54601ee1b59b87ce10bd92","tid":258120,"uid":41958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T15:56:15.000Z","msg":"n年前玩港服依家想重玩,可以入族嗎?<br />\n<br />\ngame I'd:榮少<br />\n<br />\n麻煩如可以加一加我。。"},{"pid":"a4d01cff6bde6c535f7e65593edf5d319a34a0e8","tid":258120,"uid":96732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"新玩嗰啲唔好成日要人帶<br />\n帶你唔係老奉<br />\n咩都唔想投資嘅話都係盡早放棄隻game啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1c8a3d9532984db005f3c3b8761d1872ea0774","tid":258120,"uid":82816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T17:53:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新玩嗰啲唔好成日要人帶<br />\n帶你唔係老奉<br />\n咩都唔想投資嘅話都係盡早放棄隻game啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n年年班友都係用成日黎企妖3 R人帶<br />\n到冇人帶就話隻game唔friendly <br />\n講到明去執金蓮子可以賺錢包團都冇人理<br />\n自始之後冇再